Package jtuple

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BoundTuple
    Represents a tuple whose elements type are bound to a given tuple schema.
    Tuple
    Represents a generic tuple of objects.
    Tuple.Builder
    Class used to build new tuples avoiding proliferation.
    TupleSchema
    Represents a schema used to bound the element types of a bound tuple.
    TupleSchema.Builder
    A builder class to construct new tuple schemas.
  • Exception Summary
    Exception Description
    TupleSchemaException
    Exception thrown when a tuple shema is not satisfied.
